data.description: Allow me to paint a vivid picture of the stunning three-story town hall situated in the heart of Stonecrest, completed in 2017. THIS HOME IS now ready and available to show with new carpet and vinyl.  This remarkable architectural gem is ideally positioned, mere minutes away from the vibrant Stonecrest Mall, ensuring convenience and accessibility for its residents. As you approach this town hall, you'll notice that while the floors may require a little tender loving care, this property is far from being a diamond in the rough. Instead, it is a solid stone waiting to be shaped into a magnificent masterpiece. Step inside, and you'll immediately be captivated by the spaciousness and charm that this three-story residence exudes. Spread across these levels, you'll find a variety of meticulously designed living spaces, each thoughtfully crafted to meet your every need and desire. One of the notable highlights of this town hall is the additional family room located on the upper level. This extra space offers a sanctuary for relaxation and quality time with loved ones. Whether you envision cozy movie nights, lively gatherings, or simply a peaceful retreat, this family room provides the perfect setting. Adding to the appeal of this property is the homeowner's association (HOA), which assumes responsibility for the meticulous care of the lawn and exterior. This affords you the luxury of enjoying the picturesque surroundings without the burden of maintenance. Spend your days basking in the beauty of the outdoors, hosting barbecues, or indulging in quiet contemplation in the meticulously manicured gardens. Swimming pool, tennis court and kids playground is located across the street and sister property. If you have any questions please call the listing agent.
